        <h1>Pumpkin Soup</h1>
       <div class="recipe-details">
        <img src="pumkin-soup.jpg" alt="Pumpkin Soup" class="recipe-image">
            <div class="ingredients">
            
        
                <h2>Ingredients:</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>500g pumpkin, peeled and cubed</li>
                    <li>1 onion, chopped</li>
                    <li>2 cloves garlic, minced</li>
                    <li>1 tsp ground ginger</li>
                    <li>3 cups vegetable broth</li>
                    <li>Salt and pepper to taste</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="instructions">
                <h2>Instructions:</h2>
                <ol>
                    <li>Saute onion and garlic in a pot until fragrant.</li>
                    <li>Add pumpkin cubes and ginger, stirring for 2 minutes.</li>
                    <li>Pour in the vegetable broth and bring to a boil.</li>
                    <li>Simmer for 15-20 minutes, until the pumpkin is tender.</li>
                    <li>Blend until smooth, season with salt and pepper, and serve warm.</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>
